authorized building was discovered. This action aims to prevent inflated compensation claims under the Resettlement and Rehabilitation Scheme.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/infrastructure/fir-filed-against-four-for-unlawful-constructions-on-noida-airport-expansion-land/130455591?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-18216/130455591.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "infrastructure"}]}